OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783930924
OL,3,CMore than #250m pledged to boost
OL,4,Cpolicing for Jewish communities
OL,6,FMore than #250 million is to be
OL,7,Finvested in increasing policing in
OL,8,FJewish communities after a spate of
OL,9,Fviolent antisemitic attacks in recent
OL,10,Fmonths.
OL,12,FThe increased funding will see a surge
OL,13,Fin police presence, patrols, and
OL,14,Fprotection of security outside
OL,15,Fsynagogues and schools, as well as
OL,16,Fspecialist plainclothes officers in
OL,17,FJewish communities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
