PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783930924
OL,3,CMore than #250m pledged to boost
OL,4,Cpolicing for Jewish communities
OL,6,FThe announcement follows an increase
OL,7,Fin antisemitic hate crimes, including
OL,8,Fthe stabbing of two Jewish men in
OL,9,FGolders Green, north London, in April
OL,10,Fand an arson attack at a former
OL,11,Fsynagogue in Whitechapel, central
OL,12,FLondon, in May.
OL,14,FThe national terror threat level was
OL,15,Fraised from substantial to severe in
OL,16,FApril, while Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,17,FStarmer has said tackling antisemitism
OL,18,F"has been central to my leadership
OL,19,Ffrom day one".
OL,26,@zD@AOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
