CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783930924
OL,3,CMore than #250m pledged to boost
OL,4,Cpolicing for Jewish communities
OL,6,FThe Home Office said the cash boost
OL,7,Fwill see #250 million spread out
OL,8,Facross the next three years, providing
OL,9,FJewish communities with a major boost
OL,10,Fin protection and funding efforts to
OL,11,Froot out antisemitism across society,
OL,12,Ffocusing on education, building
OL,13,Fcohesion and countering extremism.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783930924
OL,3,CMore than #250m pledged to boost
OL,4,Cpolicing for Jewish communities
OL,6,FIt will deliver more than 500
OL,7,Fadditional officers across England and
OL,8,FWales, including around 300 additional
OL,9,Fofficers in London and around 80 in
OL,10,FGreater Manchester, along with more
OL,11,Fofficers for forces serving other
OL,12,Fareas with significant Jewish
OL,13,Fpopulations.
OL,15,FThe package will also continue Project
OL,16,FServator, deploying specialist and
OL,17,Fplain-clothes officers trained to
OL,18,Fidentify suspicious behaviour and
OL,19,Fprevent serious crime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
