OL,3,CMore than #250m pledged to boost
OL,4,Cpolicing for Jewish communities
OL,6,FSir Keir said: "The rise in
OL,7,Fantisemitism we have seen in recent
OL,8,Fyears is a test of our values as a
OL,9,Fcountry and tackling it has been
OL,10,Fcentral to my leadership from day one.
OL,12,F"That is why earlier this year, I
OL,13,Fbrought together leaders from
OL,14,Fbusiness, education, health, policing
OL,15,Fand civil society at Downing Street to
OL,16,Fdrive a co-ordinated response across
OL,17,Fevery corner of our society."
OL,26,@nD@POUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
