OL,3,CMore than #250m pledged to boost
OL,4,Cpolicing for Jewish communities
OL,6,FMore than #22 million will go to
OL,7,FGreater Manchester Police to sustain
OL,8,Fthe increase in policing presence
OL,9,Ffollowing the terrorist attack at the
OL,10,FHeaton Park Hebrew Congregation
OL,11,FSynagogue last October.
OL,13,FAnd around #43 million is to be
OL,14,Fdistributed across seven other force
OL,15,Fareas with significant Jewish
OL,16,Fcommunities: Hertfordshire, Essex,
OL,17,FNorthumbria, Sussex, Thames Valley,
OL,18,FWest Midlands and West Yorkshire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
