PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783930924
OL,3,CMore than #250m pledged to boost
OL,4,Cpolicing for Jewish communities
OL,6,FThe Home Office said a further #86
OL,7,Fmillion will go to the Metropolitan
OL,8,FPolice, while #41 million will be
OL,9,Fspent on national policing co-
OL,10,Fordination and increased antisemitism
OL,11,Fcapabilities to fund antisemitism
OL,12,Ftraining for all officers in England
OL,13,Fand Wales.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, #59 million will go to
OL,16,FCounter-Terrorism Police to bolster
OL,17,Fprotective security and counter state
OL,18,Fthreats.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
