OL,3,CMore than #250m pledged to boost
OL,4,Cpolicing for Jewish communities
OL,6,FPolicing Minister Sarah Jones said:
OL,7,F"After a series of appalling attacks
OL,8,Fagainst Jewish communities, the
OL,9,Fdifficult decision was made to raise
OL,10,Fthe threat level to severe. My
OL,11,Fthoughts remain with the victims of
OL,12,Fthese vile attacks.
OL,14,F"Today we are going further and
OL,15,Fproviding record funding to help keep
OL,16,FJewish people safe, supporting visible
OL,17,Fpolicing and protection around
OL,18,Fsynagogues, schools and community
OL,19,Fcentres.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
