CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783930924
OL,3,CMore than #250m pledged to boost
OL,4,Cpolicing for Jewish communities
OL,6,F"We will do everything in our power to
OL,7,Frid society of the evil of
OL,8,Fantisemitism."
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FMet Police Deputy Commissioner Matt
OL,16,FJukes said: "Jewish communities are
OL,17,Ffacing an exceptional threat with
OL,18,Frising hate crime alongside terrorism
OL,19,Fand interference from hostile states.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@NO]xD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783930924
OL,3,CMore than #250m pledged to boost
OL,4,Cpolicing for Jewish communities
OL,6,F"We thank the Home Office for this
OL,7,Fvital funding which is set to
OL,8,Fstrengthen our ability to protect
OL,9,Fthose most at risk and relentlessly
OL,10,Fpursue those driven by hate.
OL,12,F"Antisemitic hate crime has reached a
OL,13,Ftwo-year high. We have already
OL,14,Fdeployed an additional 1,000 officers
OL,15,Feach week and Counter Terrorism
OL,16,FPolicing has made 35 arrests as part
OL,17,Fof 11 investigations.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783930924
OL,3,CMore than #250m pledged to boost
OL,4,Cpolicing for Jewish communities
OL,6,F"But short-term surge activity is not
OL,7,Fenough if we want to provide lasting
OL,8,Fprotection for communities against the
OL,9,Flong-term threats posed by hostile
OL,10,Fstates and instances of hate crime.
OL,12,F"This investment allows us to bolster
OL,13,Fexisting dedicated Community
OL,14,FProtection Teams and establish further
OL,15,Fteams across three sites in London,
OL,16,Fadvance our armed policing and
OL,17,Fspecialist Counter Terrorism teams,
OL,18,Frecruit up to 300 officers, and create
OL,19,Fa community hub in Golders Green that
OL,20,Fwill provide visible and locally-
OL,21,Frooted policing."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
